    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Update on Your Application – [Company Name]\n\nDear [Candidate Name],\n\nThank you for taking the time to meet with us during the final interview round for the [Position] role at [Company Name]. We truly appreciated the insight you shared and the enthusiasm you brought to our conversation.\n\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with another candidate who best matches our current needs. This decision was not made lightly, as we were faced with an exceptionally strong field of applicants who all demonstrated outstanding qualifications. The selection process was a whirlwind of talent and ambition, a chaotic influx of brilliance that felt almost overwhelming—like a storm of possibilities that we had to navigate with precision and care. We wanted to make sure we gave every candidate, including yourself, the attention they deserved.\n\nWe wish you the very best in your job search, and we encourage you to apply for other roles that resonate with your skills. Should you have any questions or need further clarification, feel free to reach out.\n\nSincerely,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Title]  \n[Company Name]",
